columns.name: type
columns.description: The type of analyzer, which corresponds to the zone of trust chosen for the analyzer.

columns.name: created_at
columns.description: A timestamp for the time at which the analyzer was created.

columns.name: last_resource_analyzed
columns.description: The resource that was most recently analyzed by the analyzer.

columns.name: last_resource_analyzed_at
columns.description: The time at which the most recently analyzed resource was analyzed.

columns.name: status_reason
columns.description: The statusReason provides more details about the current status of the analyzer.

columns.name: findings
columns.description: A list of findings retrieved from the analyzer that match the filter criteria specified, if any.
